Raymond Keane https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Raymond_Keane 0 Raymond Keane, born Raymond Kortz, (1906–1973) was an actor during the silent era of movies. He was tall and striking. He was the son of jeweler Harry Kortz. He died in Los Angeles. Raymond_Keane , born Raymond_Kortz , ( 1906 – 1973 ) was an_actor during the_silent_era of movies . He was tall_and_striking .
